"I think so! He self destructed. Good thing they weren't too far in the
cave." Rizopas says. Deemos raises up suddenly and starts pressing buttons
on a device.

"We beat them, but the 3 I was after got away again! Plintissam report back
here at once!" Deemos says. Testifier growled, trying to think of ideas of
how to kill Deemos and get away with it. Plintissa, inside of the cave,
jerked suddenly, and sadly walked towards the exit of the cave...
